perl-encode-locale|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
perl-encode-locale: perl-encode-locale (Determine the locale encoding)
perl-encode-locale:
perl-encode-locale: In many applications it's wise to let Perl use Unicode for the strings
perl-encode-locale: it processes.  Most of the interfaces Perl has to the outside world is
perl-encode-locale: still byte based.  Programs therefore needs to decode byte strings
perl-encode-locale: that enter the program from the outside and encode them again on the
perl-encode-locale: way out.
perl-encode-locale:
perl-encode-locale: http://search.cpan.org/dist/Encode-Locale/
perl-encode-locale:
perl-encode-locale: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
